side-effects:
Side-effects gastro-intestinal disturbances, abnormal liver
function tests; headache; rash; less commonly taste
disturbances, increased appetite; hypertension, oedema, flushing;
dizziness, paraesthesia, drowsiness; influenza-like symptoms; haematuria,
nephrolithiasis, increased urinary frequency, decreased libido; myalgia;
dermatitis, pruritus, urticaria; rarely thirst, palpitation, asthenia, nervousness, insomnia, and renal impairment
